sku gzugs dag ni khyad par du
ji ltar gsungs pa rab gnas pa
de dag don ni ngas byas pas
de rnams don ni grub zin gyi
ci bde bar ni mchod par byos
khyed kyis gsol ba btab pa bzhin
rab tu gnas par byas zin gyi
mchod pa rgyun mi 'chad pa dang
zhag bdun bar du mchod par byos
g+hi hang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman
sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas
nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi
bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal dag gyur cig
zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste
snying po rnam dag ye shes mchog rtogs nas
yon tan kun gyi dbyings su gyur pa yis
bkra shis des kyang dug gsum zhi gyur cig
dur ba tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste
rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe ni rab bsgrubs nas
nyon mongs skye shi rgyun chad gyur pa yi
bkra shis des ni tshe yang 'phel gyur cig
bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos
'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun
byang chub snying po mchog tu dag gyur pa'i
bkra shis des ni don kun 'grub par shog
dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrog pa'i tshul
ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du dag gyur te
chos rnams ma nor yongs su ston pa yi
bkra shis des kyang tshig la dbang thob shog
li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te
chos rnams ma nor dbang du bsdus nas kyang
chos kyi rgyal srid rtag tu brtan gyur pa'i
bkra shis des kyang khyed srid brtan gyur cig
yungs kar rdo rje'i rigs te thams cad du
bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms par byed pa yi
mthu stobs yon tan phun sum tshogs gyur pa'i
bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams zhi bar shog
rgyud sde yid bzhin rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs nas
rab gnas mkhas pa'i dgongs bzhed mu tig tshogs
lag tu blang bde cho ga'i srad bu la
legs par bkod 'di skal bzang mgrin pa'i rgyan
srid pa'i 'khor lo las kyi mgyogs 'gro'i tshogs
ma lus bcom pa 'od gsal gzhal med cher
rnam kun mchog ldan rdo rje'i skur bzhengs te
chos kyi dbyings la rab tu gnas byas pas
mkha' khyab sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i chu 'dzin las
dngos grub rnam gnyis 'dod dgu'i char phab ste
skye rgu phan bde'i lo thog rgyas byed shog
